{"tid":1611411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[一齊傾下]同狗正面對抗 係逼於無奈下嘅最後一步","createTime":"2019-10-02T02:58:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T10:40:38.000Z","uid":234195,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"ccb98c558259123405e21562b37afac195d1a991","tid":1611411,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:58:18.000Z","msg":"三個幾月，都見到好多次同狗打攻防戰同陣地戰。但諗深一層目的係咩？<br />\n<br />\n612就係因為要攻入去，阻二讀。但之後嘅對峙好似係為留而留，等比人清場。咁樣會導致好多人被捕，對狗嘅損傷係好低。<br />\n<br />\n大家好似因為對狗仇恨，對抗爭模式作出咗改變，變成與狗嘅正面衝突為多。但事實上，正面衝突好多時都係自己人損失慘重。<br />\n<br />\n所以如果抗爭模式變成以下咁樣會唔會好d？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">遊行/集會&mdash;&mdash;&gt;破壞主要目標&mdash;&mdash;&gt;達成目標後散水&mdash;&mdash;&gt;真係散唔到先打狗救人</span><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊諗吓！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4afab8a6905b3b46a2dead8bd2a4c2c6c21fad","tid":1611411,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:58:39.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"a28533d96966437f2c3f4f80e8131bd3e9fe9d97","tid":1611411,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:58:42.000Z","msg":"對準政權 全民公投實行雙普選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1609445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1609445</a>"},{"pid":"44094c54a92cfa437a41b66be7d1a7dcfa5dbd96","tid":1611411,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:58:49.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"459eb43332d99b06c9b5aadf1501d5130b030173","tid":1611411,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:58:59.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"88f84996c2b159304223e37efe144c0564d5b3ad","tid":1611411,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:59:09.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"82e7891abbc5ee20bf261e6a5642cfe09e450425","tid":1611411,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:59:25.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"337dfb2039d7